{"tid":2090489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兵力集中轉移印太區  澳軍費增至萬億 購導彈制衡中國","createTime":"2020-07-02T07:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T07:52:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48eac4b696c3d29703735d328710ab652ce5f48a","tid":2090489,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200702/W7PHXGVBDNIAMQHYU4PZKP2PKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200702%2FW7PHXGVBDNIAMQHYU4PZKP2PKU%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8LyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=7bea402c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200702%2FW7PHXGVBDNIAMQHYU4PZKP2PKU%2F&h=1d8421e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200702/W7PHXGVBDNIAMQHYU4PZKP2PKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n兵力集中轉移印太區 <br />\n澳軍費增至萬億 購導彈制衡中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫里森昨日公佈澳洲新國防戰略。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n澳洲跟中國的關係近期越趨緊張之際，宣佈增加未來10年國防預算至2,700億澳元（1.4萬億港元），用作擴軍，包括購買遠程彈道導彈等武器，同時會將軍力集中轉移到印太區，目標明顯旨在制衡中國。<br />\n<br />\n總理莫里森（Scott Morrison）昨日在坎培拉發表演說，指澳洲政府會先花約8億澳元（42.9億港元）從美國海軍購入AGM-158C遠程反艦導彈，以提升軍方海上打擊能力；澳軍目前仍使用1980年代初投產的AGM-84魚叉反艦導彈。此外，莫里森指遠程反艦及陸上攻擊武器、遠程火箭炮及導彈系統亦在坎培拉的購物清單上；他們還計劃發展並測試高速長程打擊武器，包括超高音速導彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qDmkJ9720Qqvwhs5iTr73qdPIac=/190x123/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2AYQX3HFM7KRG4H5SACB4CAUGQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqDmkJ9720Qqvwhs5iTr73qdPIac%3D%2F190x123%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2AYQX3HFM7KRG4H5SACB4CAUGQ.gif&h=0110e0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲是美國的印太區盟友，有派兵參與2003年的伊拉克戰爭。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sqzte6iwzp4CK_C7TW0EO0GPd1I=/190x123/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SEEKUWGCU3Y6F44VHXDA3CYPEU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsqzte6iwzp4CK_C7TW0EO0GPd1I%3D%2F190x123%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSEEKUWGCU3Y6F44VHXDA3CYPEU.gif&h=77c054c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲防長雷諾茲昨日就新國防戰略回應記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府疑遭華黑客攻擊<br />\n<br />\n莫里森又強調網絡安全是澳洲國防戰略的關鍵，揚言提升網絡攻擊力；他<br />\n................................<br />\n，路透社引述三個消息指澳洲視中國為疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲對上一次、即2016年公佈的10年國防預算有約1,950億澳元（1.04萬億港元），<br />\n..............................<br />\n，區內所有國家無論大小都可自由來往，且受國際法律及規範約束。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲洛伊國際政策研究所國際安全計劃總監羅赫芬角（Sam Roggeveen）指，<br />\n.....................................<br />\n但莫里斯昨日明言美國仍是澳洲「我們國防政策的基礎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G1XQeYIZLgw6F7-3xnGhhsTzWs8=/1072x590/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NEQVSRR6NJJYBLKH73HWIULRJY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG1XQeYIZLgw6F7-3xnGhhsTzWs8%3D%2F1072x590%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEQVSRR6NJJYBLKH73HWIULRJY.gif&h=7b87e22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n查武肺源頭成導火線<br />\n<br />\n澳洲2018年禁中國電訊商華為染指其5G網絡後，<br />\n..................................<br />\n澳洲形容舉動是經濟「威逼」。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/法新社<br />\n澳洲"}]}